um achievable level. This is used as part of a scentence so it is explicitly all lower case.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ASSISTING_HEROES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Assisting heroes</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pomagający bohaterowie</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Header for a list, is followed by the names of the heroes that assisted on a planet.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RELIC_UNLOCKED</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Relic unlocked</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Odblokowany relikt</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Used like: "Relic unlocked: NAME".</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">COMPLEXITY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Complexity</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Złożoność</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Used to describe the complexity of a certain planet, used like: "Complexity: NAME"</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TOTAL_XP</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Total experience</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Łączne doświadczenie</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Used like: "Total Experience: VALUE", used in a breakdown to summarize the total experience points the player has accumulated for a certain race or technology.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DISMISS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Dismiss</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zwolnij</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT</Data></Cel